snippet.title: The Ditzy Demons Are in Love With Me Fan Disc English Trailer
snippet.description:
Now Available on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1354640/The_Ditzy_Demons_Are_in_Love_With_Me__Fandisc/

Those ditzy demons are back once again in the fan disc for The Ditzy Demons Are in Love With Me. The fan disc contains a series of after stories featuring all the lovable heroines from the original game. What kind of antics will Riria and the rest of these ditzy demons get into? Will they have actually learned anything or is it just another day for these ditzy demons?

The Ditzy Demons Are in Love With Me Fan Disc once again features the beautiful designs of character designer, Sayori, famous for work on the NEKOPARA franchise.
